ria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xva1665703026639.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xva1665703026639.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xva1665703026639.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xva1665703026639\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Derived Field\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Derived Field is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Field. It can have a Subtype Entity or a Derived Component Entity as parent.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xva1665703026639__section_w519ab1b5b1_w520ab1b5_w521ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xva1665703026639__section_glj_mgr_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d431294e56\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"xva1665703026639__image_uwt_pgr_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_field.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fld</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"byl1665703025171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byl1665703025171.html\" title=\"A Derived Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It can be a subobject of a Modeled Entity (in which case it is known as a Subtype Entity), or of a Component or Modeled Component.\">Derived Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kgf1665703025767.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kgf1665703025767.html\" title=\"A Subtype Field references a Supertype Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\">Subtype Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aam1665702585156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aam1665702585156.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Field references a Modeled Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\">Derived Component Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xva1665703026639__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">fld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xva1665703026639__section_ry5_tgr_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d431294e278\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xva1665703026639__p_d94982e1_d94983e1_d94984e1\">Field is an abstract data type that specializes\n        Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xva1665703026639__ul_bdx_5gr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xva1665703026639__li_d37313e1_d37314e1_d37315e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xva1665703026639__p_d94985e1_d94986e1_d94987e1\">It has a Derived Entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Derived Field Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Derived Field A Derived Field is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Field. It can have a Subtype Entity or a Derived Component Entity as parent. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: fld Main Development Object? No Part of: Derived Entity Contains: Value, Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: Subtype Field , Derived Component Field Compilation output: — URI format: fld: FieldName Specialization Field is an abstract data type that specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Derived Entity as parent. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}